(14, 92, 'Air quality, noise impact assessment and modeling services', 'air-quality,-noise-impact-assessment-and-modeling-services', '<p><strong>Air quality assessment</strong></p>\r\n<p>We are expert in air quality assessment for Residential, Industrial, industrial estate, port, air port, sky train, highway and etc which include baseline condition, construction period and operation period. The mathematic models e.g. AERMET/AERMAP/AERMOD, IVE, MM5/CAMx, MUAIR, ISC, CALINE 4 and etc are used for the assessment.</p>\r\n<ul class=\"row-fluid service-detail\">\r\n<li class=\"span4\">\r\n<div><a href=\"images/Air-quality-noise-impact-assessment/image002.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" type=\"image/jpeg\" class=\"jcepopup\" data-mediabox=\"group[img]\"><img src=\"images/Air-quality-noise-impact-assessment/image002.jpg\" alt=\"image002\" /></a></div>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"span4\">\r\n<div><a href=\"images/Air-quality-noise-impact-assessment/image004.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" type=\"image/jpeg\" class=\"jcepopup\" data-mediabox=\"group[img]\"><img src=\"images/Air-quality-noise-impact-assessment/image004.jpg\" alt=\"image004\" /></a></div>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"span4\">\r\n<div><a href=\"images/Air-quality-noise-impact-assessment/image006.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" type=\"image/jpeg\" class=\"jcepopup\" data-mediabox=\"group[img]\"><img src=\"images/Air-quality-noise-impact-assessment/image006.jpg\" alt=\"image006\" /></a></div>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul class=\"row-fluid service-detail\">\r\n<ul class=\"row-fluid service-detail\">\r\n<li class=\"span4\">\r\n<div><a href=\"images/Air-quality-noise-impact-assessment/image008.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" type=\"image/jpeg\" class=\"jcepopup\" data-mediabox=\"group[img]\"><img src=\"images/Air-quality-noise-impact-assessment/image008.jpg\" alt=\"image008\" /></a></div>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"span4\">\r\n<div><a href=\"images/Air-quality-noise-impact-assessment/image009.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" type=\"image/jpeg\" class=\"jcepopup\" data-medi